Pathogen identification by shotgun metagenomics of patients with necrotizing 
soft-tissue infections.

Rodriguez C(1)(2)(3), Jary A(1), Hua C(4), Woerther PL(1), Bosc R(5), Desroches 
M(1), Sitterlé E(6), Gricourt G(3), De Prost N(1)(2), Pawlotsky JM(1)(2), 
Chosidow O(4)(7), Sbidian E(4)(7), Decousser JW(1); Multidisciplinary 
Necrotizing Fasciitis Study Group.

Author information:
(1)Department of Microbiology, AP-HP, Henri Mondor University Hospital, 
Université Paris-Est, Créteil, France.
(2)INSERM U955, AP-HP, Henri Mondor University Hospital, Université Paris-Est, 
Créteil, France.
(3)NGS Platform, IMRB Institute, AP-HP, Henri Mondor University Hospital, 
Université Paris-Est, Créteil, France.
(4)Department of Dermatology, AP-HP, Henri Mondor University Hospital, 
