Air pollution is not 'the new smoking': comparing the disease burden of air 
pollution and smoking across the globe, 1990-2017.

Gao W(1), Sanna M(2), Hefler M(3), Wen CP(4)(5).

Author information:
(1)Master's Program in Global Health and Development, Taipei Medical University, 
Taipei, Taiwan waynegao@tmu.edu.tw cwengood@nhri.edu.tw.
(2)Master's Program in Global Health and Development, Taipei Medical University, 
Taipei, Taiwan.
